Class ReplicationEndpoint

    public final class ReplicationEndpoint
extends Object
implements org.apache.activemq.core.protocol.core.ChannelHandler, org.apache.activemq.core.server.ActiveMQComponent
    Handles all the synchronization necessary for replication on the backup side (that is the backup's side of the "remote backup" use case).

    Clebert Suconic
